feat.value: A lacuna of 2 pages (1 folio) exists between this document and the end of the previous extant fragment of this codex (MONB.XJ 62); the lacuna has a parallel witness in MONB.GL 53 1.8-54 2.13 (published as urn:cts:copticLit:shenoute.eagerness.monbgl_53_54). The text in this document immediately continues in MONB.XJ 77.
